  <conbody>
    <p id="task-definition"><term>Tasks</term><indexterm>DITA task</indexterm> answer   &quot;How do I?&quot; questions. They describe what steps to take  in order to achieve a particular aim. The task is a <xref href="dita-specialization-serna-free.xml">specialization</xref> of the <xref href="generic-topic-serna-free.xml">generic topic</xref>.

</p>
